extends java.lang.Object
implements IErn<Store>, IJson<org.json.JSONObject>, IDealer<Store>, android.os.Parcelable

    This class is a representation of a store as the API v2 exposes it

    More documentation available on via our Store Reference documentation, on the engineering blog.

        public Dealer getDealer()
        Get the Dealer which is (or rather should be, but this is not guaranteed) related to this store.

        The dealer-object is not automatically set by the SDK. The developer, needs to get the dealer resource from getDealerUrl(), and then add it with setDealer(Dealer).
